description: {"blocks":[{"key":"2g80j","text":"This protocol is to be used after you mastered setting up a MinION sequencing run (dx.doi.org/10.17504/protocols.io.4r3l2oy53v1y/v3) using the rapid sequencing kit from Nanopore (SQK-RAD004). It contains all steps and material need for a successful run. This kit is recommended for rapid preparation time for several different DNA samples that will be run together (equivalent to multiplexing) and limited laboratory equipment. The output is lower than that generated by the ligation sequencing kit.
